{"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "title": "Shin Seiki Evangelion", "title_uuid": "cc3209cd-c119-4870-b06c-9a34f447db7e", "volume": "Shin Seiki Evangelion 8", "volume_uuid": "124c200f-cec3-4206-b045-d38a438222b9", "pages": [{"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 2757, "img_height": 1196, "blocks": [{"box": [107, 380, 379, 830], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["貞本義行", "よく物語の主人公は作者のキャラクター", "お、初回の二人公はドロック・ターを写し出す鏡のようなものだといわせます。", "いわれます。", "それに、その確かにそれは少なからずあるかもし", "頭がにくいはショッピングなのですが、れないけど、時としてギャップに苦しかけません", "お事もある。", "もし事の幼さ。私の幼き頃の母の記憶といえば、このローデーショームは、", "１００円ブラモ欲しさに母のおま】が", "「ビビリングに飛びているのは、ら小銭を盗んだのがばれて建てかけできるように", "ジャンリ数を曲げるのは、ここのの家の柱にローブで縛り付けられ、ユーザームをお", "大工に笑われながら日がな１日泣き", "はらした記憶が蘇る。", "．．．まさにこれこそ無償の愛！", "母上っ、おかげであなたの息子はま", "っすぐ育ちましたよ〜〜〜っ。"]}, {"box": [1131, 769, 1335, 852], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["２０１６年１１月２８日"]}, {"box": [17, 1143, 193, 1176], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["装備・無注忠広＂ＢＥＥＮＴＯ"]}, {"box": [963, 999, 1173, 1055], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["貴本"]}, {"box": [1114, 1050, 1327, 1123], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＹＤＳＨＯ", "原作、ＧＡＴＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [1543, 63, 1763, 310], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["１９８０年１月２０１８年１０月１９日、１９２０年"]}, {"box": [1821, 46, 2120, 129], "vertical": false, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["ＩＳＢＮ４－Ｏ４－７１３５２９－", "ＣＯ９７９¥５４０Ｅ"]}, {"box": [1822, 183, 2152, 218], "vertical": false, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["定価本体も４０円（税制）角川書店"]}, {"box": [1391, 148, 1448, 616], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["新世紀ーーーッッッ"]}, {"box": [1372, 806, 1455, 1105], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["盲貞本穀行", "原作ＧＡＩＮＡＸ"]}], "img_path": "eva08-001.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1745, "img_height": 1196, "blocks": [{"box": [264, 315, 549, 350], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ＷｏｒｄｏｋｉｅｖａＣｏｎｆｉｃｓＡ"]}, {"box": [147, 414, 636, 621], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["新世紀", "アンゲリオン", "エヴァ", "貞本義行", "「義行"]}, {"box": [828, 172, 904, 633], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["新規エヴァンゲリオン"]}, {"box": [336, 624, 469, 656], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["原作ＧＡＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [266, 722, 537, 761], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["Ｙｏｓｉｌｉｇｈｔ（・ＳＡＤＡＮＯＴＯ"]}, {"box": [828, 795, 898, 1079], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["原作ＧＡＩＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [830, 785, 909, 1084], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["囂貞本義行"]}], "img_path": "eva08-002.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 823, "img_height": 1191, "blocks": [{"box": [49, 1083, 355, 1123], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}], "img_path": "eva08-003.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 823, "img_height": 1191, "blocks": [{"box": [658, 60, 682, 154], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["どこだ？"]}, {"box": [116, 148, 140, 222], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ここ．．．"]}, {"box": [676, 294, 715, 414], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["何だこれ？"]}, {"box": [137, 878, 244, 1087], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["僕は初号機の", "エントリープラグに", "居たはずなのに"]}], "img_path": "eva08-004.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 823, "img_height": 1191, "blocks": [{"box": [411, 72, 468, 157], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["あれは．．．", "僕だ"]}, {"box": [88, 524, 148, 612], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["僕が泣い", "泣いてる"]}, {"box": [544, 661, 602, 760], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["誰かが", "泣いてる．．．"]}, {"box": [399, 733, 453, 799], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["そして", "あれは"]}, {"box": [63, 1022, 97, 1117], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["父さん？"]}], "img_path": "eva08-005.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 823, "img_height": 1191, "blocks": [{"box": [698, 47, 762, 187], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["行かないでよ", "父さん"]}, {"box": [460, 76, 511, 175], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["わがままを", "言うな"]}, {"box": [334, 97, 394, 255], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["伯父さんの所で", "いい子にしていろ"]}, {"box": [234, 36, 301, 130], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["母さんは", "どこ？"]}, {"box": [60, 91, 155, 211], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["母さんは", "どこに", "行ったの！？"]}, {"box": [568, 396, 637, 536], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["僕を置いてか", "ないで！"]}, {"box": [718, 831, 742, 947], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ウソじゃない"]}, {"box": [412, 605, 471, 684], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["母さんは", "死んだ"]}, {"box": [308, 823, 337, 896], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["そこだ"]}, {"box": [77, 583, 120, 733], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ウソだ！！"]}, {"box": [646, 871, 698, 1028], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["おまえも見ていた", "はずだ"]}, {"box": [110, 951, 165, 1031], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["後ろを", "見てみろ"]}], "img_path": "eva08-006.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 823, "img_height": 1191, "blocks": [], "img_path": "eva08-007.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 823, "img_height": 1191, "blocks": [{"box": [435, 51, 476, 126], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["母さん"]}, {"box": [685, 455, 711, 529], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["ちがう"]}, {"box": [280, 538, 305, 610], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["これは"]}, {"box": [101, 718, 130, 782], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["シンジ"]}, {"box": [233, 1007, 256, 1096], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["エヴァだ"]}], "img_path": "eva08-008.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 823, "img_height": 1191, "blocks": [{"box": [604, 55, 663, 175], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["これに乗って", "戦え"]}, {"box": [422, 26, 447, 121], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["イヤだ！！"]}, {"box": [237, 62, 302, 160], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["なんだよ", "今頃"]}, {"box": [55, 288, 141, 424], "vertical": true, "font_size":